Embedded Video System
    Display live video to LCD screen
    Capture picture by camera(triggered by button or remote controller)
    Store the picture to JPEG file
    Browser & display stored pictures in LCD screen
    Browser pictures from remote PC(using ethernet)
    Detect live object in the video. Ring the alarm(by using PMW buzzer)

